name:                EPrint
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            Text layout formatter / pretty printer
-- description:         
-- homepage:            https://github.com/mihajek/eprint
license:             BSD3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Michal HÃ¡jek
maintainer:          mihajek@gmail.com
